caption:
New French Cafe in Scottsdale, Arizona ☕️

@sweetparis just opened up in Scottsdale Quarter. They are a chain originally from Texas, with this being their first Arizona location. There's a beautiful shaded area on the sidewalk to enjoy some fun treats as well as inside. They specialize in crepes, sandwiches, waffles, and coffee. 

Here's what we got:
☕️ Nutella latte 
🍵 Strawberry Matcha 
🍦 Reeses Milkshake 
🥂 Mimosa tower
🍹Frozen mimosa
🧀 Croque Madame crepe
🥑 Le California crepe
🍫 S'mores crepe
🍅 Caprese panini
🍎 Apple cinnamon creme brulee waffle

📍15147 N Scottsdale Rd #133, Scottsdale, AZ 85254

This place was fantastic! The waffles were so light and airy. The crepes had good flavors, and they have great service!
